    'en_US' => '<p><strong><em>Journal</em></strong><strong><em> of </em></strong><strong><em>Sustainability</em></strong><strong><em>, </em></strong><strong><em>Heritage</em></strong><strong><em> and </em></strong><strong><em>Tourism</em></strong> is a semiannual academic publication of open access for the dissemination of quality scientific works, which realize contributions of interest for the advance of knowledge on tourism and hospitality. It is a magazine open to the diverse&nbsp; methodological and theoretical approaches that analyze the tourism sector, publishing original works (research articles, but also essays and reviews) that can have impact for both the academic community as well as for companies and agents.</p>
